page.title: 14A DAY IN THE LIFE-MICHELLE
page.content: On a Saturday I get up at about seven o'clock and have breakfast.After breakfast I go to the swimming pool on my bicycle.Usually I practice floating and diving.The swimming pool is really good.After swimming I go home for lunch and after that I go to ballet. There are four classes between ten a.m. and two p.m.After ballet I go swimming again.For tea I have a hot meal and after that I watch television.At half past seven I go upstairs,wash,clean my teeth get changed and read.At half past eight I say my prayers and go to sleep.I think that Woodhall Spa is a great place to live if you like activity clubs.
